Clé de Peau Beauté, the global luxury skincare and makeup brand from Shiseido Co., Ltd., was founded in 1982 with a sole objective; to forge a new frontier in advanced skin cell science, becoming the key that unlocks skin’s most radiant potential. Guided by an exquisite Japanese aesthetic sensibility and intelligence, the brand combines cutting-edge science with modernity and enchantment. Available in 27 countries and regions worldwide, Clé de Peau Beauté’s mission is to unlock the power of radiance within every woman.
